 und Geschlechtergeschichte des Ersten Weltkriegs in Österreich-Ungarn.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 08. Jun 2020) 0aHistoryxHistorical PeriodsxModern History. 7aHISTORY / Modern / 20th Century.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertE-BOOK GESAMTPAKET / COMPLETE PACKAGE 2013z9783110317350oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertE-BOOK PAKET GESCHICHTE, POLITIKWISS., SOZIOLOGIE  2013z9783110317114oZDB-23-DPS40uhttps://doi.org/10.7767/boehlau.9783205790693423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9783205790693.jpg  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-DGGb2013  aZDB-23-DPSb2013